Preserved is a music track that is unlocked near the Fossil Island Volcano, in the southern half of the Tar Swamp, or on Lithkren.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • There is an unlisted song which combines both Preservation and Preserved, beginning with Preserved.
  • According to data crowdsourced via RuneLite, approximately 71% of players unlock the track at the Volcano, 18% unlock it on Lithkren, and 11% unlock it in the Tar Swamp.

'''Preserved''' is a [[music]] track that is unlocked near the [[Fossil Island Volcano]], in the southern half of the [[Tar Swamp]], or on [[Lithkren]].

==Trivia==
*There is an unlisted song which combines both [[Preservation]] and Preserved, beginning with Preserved.
*According to data [[RuneScape:Crowdsourcing|crowdsourced]] via [[RuneLite]], approximately 71% of players unlock the track at the Volcano, 18% unlock it on Lithkren, and 11% unlock it in the Tar Swamp.
